title: Today Is Perfect - Jordy Smith
description: O'Neill's Jordy Smith is known for his cutting-edge high performance surfing. Surfing kept Jordy off the streets and he has never forgotten his roots. Now he's paying it forward. Watch Jordy Smith's perfect day. More info go to http://www.oneill.com/todayisperfect (eu only)
